downloadTitle: Dynamics 365 for Field Service and Project Service Automation Sample Data v3
downloadDescription: The Field and Project Service sample data package installs the "Fabrikam Manufacturing Master Data" v(3.0.0.0) solution along with approximately 4.5k records across 48 entities
detailsSection:
To become familiar with Dynamics 265 for Field Service and Project Service Automation, it's useful to have a small, pre-configured dataset that makes it easy to trace through end to end scenarios.

For this purpose, we've created seperate sample data installation packages(English-language only at this time) that makes it easier to explore and learn about these applications.
Running this install installation package will provide:
1)  Setup data which will default the behaviour of Field and Project Service
2) sample data such as Bookable Resources, Roles, Sales and Cost Price lists, Org Units and other reference data

IMPORTANT: This package should only be used on demonstration, evaluation, training and test systems. There is no way to un-install this sample data.
systemRequirementsSection: Microsoft Dynamics 365 (v9.0) with Field Service (v8+) and Project Service Automation(v3+)
installInstructionSection:
Please visit "https://aka.ms/fpsrefdata" for the latest and greatest instructions.
Download the self-extracting file, extract the contents to a working folder and update necessary configuration files in the PkgFolder sub-folder following the instructions from the above link.
